<style>
  :root {
    --text: #333333;
    --muted: #64748b;
    --accent: #040F2B;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --border: #e2e8f0;
    --radius: 14px;
    --shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    --speed: 250ms;
  }

  .faq-wrap {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 72px auto;
    padding: 0 20px 80px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .faq-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    color: var(--text);
    position: relative;
  }

  {% comment %} .faq-title::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    margin: 14px auto 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), #040F2B);
    border-radius: 4px;
  } {% endcomment %}

  .faq {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--card);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow var(--speed) ease, transform var(--speed) ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .faq-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    text-align: left;
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: color var(--speed) ease;
  }

  .faq-btn:hover {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .faq-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid #0A2647;
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .chev {
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.9;
    transition: transform var(--speed) ease, opacity var(--speed) ease;
  }

  .faq-item[aria-expanded="true"] .chev {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .faq-panel {
    padding: 0 24px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition:
      max-height var(--speed) ease,
      visibility 0s linear var(--speed),
      padding-bottom var(--speed) ease;
  }

  .faq-item[aria-expanded="true"] .faq-panel {
    visibility: visible;
    padding-bottom: 22px;
    transition:
      max-height var(--speed) ease,
      visibility 0s linear 0s,
      padding-bottom var(--speed) ease;
  }

  .faq-panel p {
  margin: 0;
  padding-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .faq-panel a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .faq-panel a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

<main class="faq-wrap">
  <h1 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <section class="faq" data-accordion="single" aria-label="FAQ list">
    <article class="faq-item" aria-expanded="false">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-controls="p1" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>What services do you offer?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-panel" id="p1" role="region">
        <p>We provide end-to-end recruitment and staffing solutions — from sourcing and screening to onboarding and payroll management.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item" aria-expanded="false">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-controls="p2" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>What industries do you specialize in?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-panel" id="p2" role="region">
        <p>We specialize in professional, technical, and administrative roles across multiple industries such as IT, Finance, Marketing, Sales, Engineering, and Operations. We tailor our approach based on your sector and requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item" aria-expanded="false">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-controls="p3" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How do you source candidates?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-panel" id="p3" role="region">
        <p>We use a combination of targeted job postings, referral networks, talent databases, and proactive headhunting. Our recruitment specialists also leverage professional platforms and industry connections to find the best candidates.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item" aria-expanded="false">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-controls="p4" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How long does the hiring process take?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-panel" id="p4" role="region">
        <p>Timelines depend on the role and level of specialization. For most positions, shortlisting begins within a few days. We provide regular updates and aim to deliver qualified candidates as quickly as possible.</p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item" aria-expanded="false">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-controls="p5" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Can you handle onboarding and HR administration?</span>
        <svg class="chev" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-panel" id="p5" role="region">
        <p>Yes. We offer managed services that include onboarding, compliance, payroll, and employee relations support — ensuring a smooth and hassle-free experience for both clients and hired talent.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</main>

<script>
  (() => {
    const root = document.querySelector('.faq');
    const single = root?.dataset.accordion === 'single';

    const toggle = (item, force) => {
      const btn = item.querySelector('.faq-btn');
      const panel = item.querySelector('.faq-panel');
      const open = typeof force === 'boolean' ? force : item.getAttribute('aria-expanded') !== 'true';
      item.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open);
      btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open);
      panel.style.maxHeight = open ? panel.scrollHeight + 'px' : '0px';
    };

    const closeAll = (except) => {
      if (!single) return;
      root.querySelectorAll('.faq-item[aria-expanded="true"]').forEach(it => {
        if (it !== except) toggle(it, false);
      });
    };

    root.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(it => {
      const btn = it.querySelector('.faq-btn');
      const panel = it.querySelector('.faq-panel');
      it.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
      panel.style.maxHeight = '0px';
    });

    root.addEventListener('click', e => {
      const btn = e.target.closest('.faq-btn');
      if (!btn) return;
      const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
      closeAll(item);
      toggle(item);
    });

    window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item[aria-expanded="true"] .faq-panel')
        .forEach(p => p.style.maxHeight = p.scrollHeight + 'px');
    });
  })();
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CWGP - FAQ (Modern)",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "CWGP FAQ - Modern" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
